#: ../content/index.rst:27
msgid "The admin screens for a number of object types are enhanced by a new widget. The widget allows importing and exporting data for the respective object type. Shown below are the group and the role group relations as examples."
msgstr ""

#: ../content/index.rst:29
msgid "For importing data, select the respective file in the file picker and click on the import button. Then an overview screen over the data to be imported is shown. The user can exclude data from import there."
msgstr ""

#: ../content/index.rst:31
msgid "Likewise, the export shows an overview screen on which data to export. The data can be selected as well."
msgstr ""

